Name:
    An R package for the integration of cancer genomic and transcriptomic data
Description:
    ASTUTE is an R package designed to integrate genomic and transcriptomic data in order to perform genotype-phenotype mapping. It leverages regularized regression with LASSO penalty to uncover associations between somatic mutations and gene expression profiles.
